* Description

  This repository is for CM10.1 on Samsung Galaxy SIII Mini a.k.a Samsung Golden.
  It's still a work in progress.

* How To Build CM10.1 for Samsung Golden

  - Make a workspace

  $ mkdir -p ~/cyanogenmod/system
  $ cd ~/cyanogenmod/system


  - Do repo init & sync

  $ repo init -u git://github.com/CyanogenMod/android.git -b cm-10.1


  - Create .repo/local_manifests/roomservice.xml with the following content:

  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
  <manifest>
      <project name="OliverG96/android_device_samsung_golden" path="device/samsung/golden" />
      <project name="OliverG96/android_device_samsung_golden-common" path="device/samsung/golden-common" />
      <project name="OliverG96/android_device_samsung_u8500-common" path="device/samsung/u8500-common" />
      <project name="OliverG96/android_kernel_samsung_golden" path="kernel/samsung/golden" />
      <project name="OliverG96/android_vendor_samsung_golden" path="vendor/samsung/golden" />
      <project name="TeamCanjica/android_hardware_u8500" path="hardware/u8500" />
  </manifest>

  $ repo sync


  - Setup vendor

  $ ./vendor/cm/get-prebuilts


  - Setup environment

  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ lunch cm_golden-eng


  - Build CM10.1

  $ export USE_CCACHE=1
  $ make -j4 bacon


